            <title><![CDATA[#动物内脏是不是垃圾食品# 不一定！猪肝、鸡心、鸡胗、毛肚、猪肾（猪腰子）这5种很值得吃[馋嘴]！《中国居民膳食指南（2022版）》中表明，内脏食物中含有丰富的...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E5%86%85%E8%84%8F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E5%86%85%E8%84%8F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#动物内脏是不是垃圾食品#</span></a> 不一定！猪肝、鸡心、鸡胗、毛肚、猪肾（猪腰子）这5种很值得吃<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>！<br><br>《中国居民膳食指南（2022版）》中表明，内脏食物中含有丰富的脂溶性维生素、B族维生素、铁、硒和锌等，适量摄入可弥补日常膳食不足，但多数内脏产品胆固醇含量偏高，建议每月可食用动物内脏食物2-3次，且每次不要过多。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a> （广东疾控）<br><br>一个小问题，你喜欢吃内脏吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="http://t.cn/A6Wn9SCc" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
